{"tid":439598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男警多次於警署爆格賴佔中  今被判囚21個月","createTime":"2017-10-18T02:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T03:00:17.000Z","uid":136994,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ae67a72b05d1adcd26ad9062d740cb770ff87ac8","tid":439598,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171018/57345964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171018%2F57345964&d=Fp0gW9q2H3tmsIhTXVHjeUjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=05f47780\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171018%2F57345964&h=c47d8dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171018/57345964</a><br />\n<br />\n加入警隊一年的男警在得悉同袍於警署內儲物櫃密碼鎖的密碼後，去年6月多次偷偷打開同袍的儲物櫃先後共偷去1,300元。他早前在區院承認偷竊罪，求情指受訓期間正值佔領運動，加上籌備婚禮及工作壓力等患上抑鬱，法官今判被告入獄21個月。<br />\n<br />\n律師求情時指，被告劉智偉(27歲)的報告透露，被告受婚姻和工作壓力影響，加上佔中期間要在警局候命，此時法官練錦鴻回應指：「即係工作啫」，律師又透露被告患有適應障礙，現已認錯知錯，向家人、事主及警隊致歉，而被告犯案不是因財政困難，只是貪念和以犯案以舒緩壓力，被告願意賠償及承擔法律責任，重犯機會低，亦得到家人支持，被告望獲輕判以盡快出獄回報社會。<br />\n<br />\n被告早前承認於去年6月底某天至7月8日期間，在友翔道油麻地警署5樓一間男儲物櫃室，先後3次偷取共1,300元現金，及後同袍暗中在儲物櫃安裝攝錄器而揭發被告於7月9日在同一地方企圖偷竊。"},{"pid":"3d866cfb9afd2f5e310fccd4218b5c605d9d18f5","tid":439598,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:57:48.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84dfec79da42370408813aa4e3b9725576b1be85","tid":439598,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:59:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed7f6fa5709de883792a113037f8a02acf46d07","tid":439598,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:00:04.000Z","msg":"27嵗坐監 gg"},{"pid":"16b1804b9fe992cf146d7b4624dae101a7d4dab4","tid":439598,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}